data.description: Follow the clover through the fruit trees to the Enchanted ''Secret Garden'' to this North West Quintessential Cottage. A sanctuary ''Hidden'' on the west side...a ''Tiny Home'' scale sanctuary for people & wildlife. Soaring ceilings, maple kitchen and a sleeping loft. It is absolutely enchanting & peaceful...a rare offering. Plus... there is room off the rear alley to build an additional home with garage!!
